    io.jenetics.BitChromosome.toSeq()
    io.jenetics.Chromosome.toSeq()
    Since the chromosome itself extends the BaseSeq, it is no longer necessary to get a sequence with genes. If it is necessary to create an ISeq from a chromosome, use ISeq.of(chromosome) instead. This method will be removed in the next major release.
    io.jenetics.AbstractChromosome.toSeq()
    io.jenetics.Genotype.toSeq()
    Since the genotype itself extends the BaseSeq, it is no longer necessary to get a sequence with genes. If it is necessary to create an ISeq from a genotype, use ISeq.of(genotype) instead. This method will be removed in the next major release.
